          "reviewBody": "Manav Rachna offers an exceptional learning environment from toddlers onwards. Its modern infrastructure includes spacious classrooms, a dedicated sports academy, and a life skills area. Teachers are dedicated and passionate, fostering both academic growth and personal development. They employ innovative teaching methods that engage students and encourage critical thinking. The school's supportive staff creates a nurturing community where every child feels valued. Overall, Manav Rachna excels in providing a holistic education that prepares students for future success.",
