            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "School life is one of the best phases of one’s life. I am fortunate to have access to education and schooling. I have learnt so much so far in the school. It was so much fun to read and learn new subjects and gain knowledge from them. I loved all my teachers and classmates. They all have given so much love and understanding to me and always helped me to achieve my goals in school. I also loved the extra-curricular activities I took part into. Be it declamation, drawing or poetry competition, I have loved all of them. I was fortunate to receive appreciation from my teachers and principal. I love coming to school and wait eagerly to be with teachers and friends there.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
