            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My son passed out from MRIS-14 a few years back and our overall experience with the school was nothing short of amazing. The teachers are knowledgeable and very helpful. The infrastructure is top notch. They also offer a lot of extracurricular opportunities in fields of music, sports, tech, etc.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
