            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I think Manav Rachna is quite the school to enroll your kids into it promotes all kind of sports and  also focuses on studies, proper material is provided to students to practise, extra classes are taken if child suffers in specific subject. Teachers are understanding and provide help when required overall faculty is also quite nice they do not force the kids to study in a boring manner they rather believe in making studying interesting so kids can clear their own concepts",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Manav Rachna International School - Sector 21C"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Deepshikha Satija"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-07-07",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "MRIS has provided such a conducive environment to both of our children, that not just they are excelling academically but in co curricular and extra curricular as well. This school provides so many opportunities for the holistic development of its students. We are glad we took the call to enroll them here after our return from USA.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Manav Rachna International School - Sector 21C"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Nikhil Bhardwaj"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-07-07",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My child has thrived at MRIS 14 school, Faridabad,  benefiting greatly from its diverse curriculum that includes robust media studies and engaging tinkering activities. Our experience with school has been exceptional over the past 12 years. The school's facilities for these subjects are impressive, providing modern equipments and resources that encourage creativity and hands-on learning. The media lab offers state-of-the-art editing software and equipment, while the tinkering sessions feature advanced tools for practical experimentation. These resources have enriched my child's educational journey, fostering both technical skills and innovative thinking. Overall, the school excels in providing a dynamic learning environment tailored to nurturing varied interests and talents.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Manav Rachna International School - Sector 21C"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Mridu Baweja"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-07-07",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I am writing this to let u know how pleased i am with the education of my son. Children seem to be inspired to do well and i believe the school is standing out as the best school in town. I like that there is discipline and rules. I’ve seen a big improvement in my son’s behaviour. So all credit goes to the school and its team.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Manav Rachna International School - Sector 21C"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Shweta Sharma"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-07-07",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "MRIS 14 school wows with project-based learning, nurturing critical thinking and collaboration - essential 21st Century Skills. Tech is skillfully woven into lessons, and the modern facilities create a vibrant learning space.  Inclusion is at the heart of their approach, ensuring all students thrive.  Academics are top-notch, but don't miss the fantastic sports programs that round out the experience!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Manav Rachna International School - Sector 21C"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Gayetri Parashar"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-07-06",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "As a parent, my school experience has been a journey of rediscovery. Watching my child navigate through their educational journey brings back memories of my own school days. The joy on their face when they grasp a new concept or make a new friend is priceless. Helping with homework has become a bonding activity, and attending school events allows me to engage with the community. It's a privilege to witness their growth and to support them in their academic and social endeavors, fostering a love for learning that I hope will last a lifetime",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
